{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dbe0d9a2b8","title":"给李静蓉的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"52522675f3","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":8,"articleId":"dbe0d9a2b8"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"fb28502ef9","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dbe0d9a2b8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"志成，即郭志成，郭亮、李灿英之子。"}],"contents":[{"id":"232d963d86","type":"title","text":"给李静蓉“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dbe0d9a2b8"},{"id":"fb28502ef9","type":"paragraph","text":"灿英同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dbe0d9a2b8"},{"id":"dcd8e687d8","type":"paragraph","text":"去年十一月十三日来信收到，极为欣感。在莫斯科时曾看见志成，情形是好的，大约不要很久可以毕业回国。你在湖南工作很好，如工作需要，不必来北京。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dbe0d9a2b8"},{"id":"c901f2209c","type":"paragraph","text":"此复，顺祝健康！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dbe0d9a2b8"},{"id":"b0abc367ff","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dbe0d9a2b8"},{"id":"2ecc37fb35","type":"paragraph","text":"五月八日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dbe0d9a2b8"},{"id":"0c56a863c1","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]李静蓉，原名李灿英，郭亮的夫人。郭亮，湖南早期的工人运动领导人之一，曾任湖南省总工会委员长、中共湖南省委书记、中共湖北省委书记、中共湘鄂赣边特委书记，1928年晒性。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dbe0d9a2b8"}],"page":{"id":"a5672d4789","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"dbe0d9a2b8","start":361,"end":361}}}},"__N_SSG":true}